s well as other experimental results featuring\nmultiple advantages of our technique. In combination with various light\nsources, including synchrotron radiation, our methodology and instrumentation\noffer new opportunities for high-resolution ARPES in the physical and life\nsciences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 May 2021 15:40:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
